data.description: Stunning Residence on a Spacious 0.4-Acre Lot in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Sacramento! This beautiful home boasts a prime corner location and an expansive 0.4-acre lot. It features an exceptional double RV Access and can accommodate up to 12 vehicles. The recently remodeled kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, showcasing brand-new laminate flooring, pristine granite countertops, and freshly painted cabinets. The bedrooms and living areas are adorned with gorgeous original hardwood floors, adding timeless charm and warmth to the interior.    Step outside into the vast backyard oasis, where you'll find a custom gate, inviting gazebo, a well-appointed built-in bar, a charming playhouse/doghouse, and so much more. With ample space available, you can create your dream garden, consider adding an ADU/second home, or set up a workshop to suit your specific needs. This exceptional property offers endless possibilities for both relaxation and expansion.
